collection.name: Meta Legends
collection.description:
Our goal is to create a complete ecosystem with the [Meta Connect](https://meta-connect.io/) app (available in Q2) and a full metaverse experience, [Meta Life](https://www.meta-life.io/metaverse).

Discover the gameplay of Meta Life with an Unreal 5 Engine [Preview](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aIeu5AqFqQ4).

Grab your Legend and join the [Legends Zone](https://legends-zone.meta-legends.com/) now!
